-brand"><a href="/">Jane Doe</a></h1><p class="rail-positioning">I build accessible, pixel-perfect experiences for the web.</p><nav class="rail-nav" aria-label="Primary"><ul><li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li><li><a href="/projects/">Work</a></li><li><a href="/about/">About</a></li><li><a href="/contact/">Contact</a></li></ul></nav></div><div class="rail-socials" aria-label="Social profiles"><a href="https://github.com/janedoe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/janedoe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></div></aside><main class="content"><section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction"><div class="hero-anchor"><strong>4.2k+</strong><span>GitHub stars</span><em>— on Signal Forge</em></div><p class="hero-employers">Previously at <span>Apple · Klaviyo</span></p><p class="hero-summary">Jane builds accessible, pixel-perfect interfaces for large-scale products.</p><a class="hero-cta " href="mailto:jane@example.test">Let&#x27;s work together</a></section><section aria-label="Selected work"><div class="section-head"><span class="section-eyebrow">Selected work</span><h2>Recent projects</h2></div><ol class="case-list"><li class="case-card"><div class="case-num">01</div><div class="case-body"><h3 class="case-title"><a href="/projects/signal-forge/">Signal Forge</a></h3><p class="case-byline">Open-source project · 4.2k stars · 23 contributors</p><p class="case-desc">Signal Forge assembles GitHub evidence into a defensible portfolio.</p><ul class="case-outcomes" aria-label="Project outcomes"><li class="outcome-pill"><b>4.2k</b><span>GitHub stars</span></li><li class="outcome-pill"><b>500+</b><span>Active users</span></li></ul><ul class="case-tags" aria-label="Tech stack"><li class="case-tag">TypeScript</li><li class="case-tag">Next.js</li><li class="case-tag">Drizzle</li></ul></div></li><figure class="quote-block"><blockquote class="quote-text">“Working with her changed how we ship — the kind of engineer whose taste you feel in the product.”</blockquote><figcaption class="quote-attr"><strong><a href="https://example.test/alex" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Alex Example</a></strong><span>VP Engineering · Acme</span></figcaption></figure></ol></section></main></div><script>(function(){var b=document.querySelector('[data-signal-theme-toggle]');if(!b)return;b.addEventListener('click',function(){var h=document.documentElement;var cur=h.getAttribute('data-theme')==='light'?'dark':'light';h.setAttribute('data-theme',cur);try{localStorage.setItem('signal-theme',cur);}catch(e){}});})();</script></body></html>"
`;

