section><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="section-header"><h2>What collaborators say</h2><p>Quotes from people I&#x27;ve worked with directly.</p></div><div class="carousel" role="region" aria-label="Testimonials"><figure class="testimonial-card"><blockquote class="testimonial-quote">“Working with her changed how we ship — the kind of engineer whose taste you feel in the product.”</blockquote><figcaption class="testimonial-author"><div class="testimonial-meta"><strong><a href="https://example.test/alex" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Alex Example</a></strong><span>VP Engineering · Acme</span></div></figcaption></figure></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="section-header"><h2>What I work on</h2><p>Grouped by where I spend the most time.</p></div><ul class="services-grid"><li class="service-card"><h4>Languages</h4><p>TypeScript</p></li><li class="service-card"><h4>Frameworks</h4><p>Next.js</p></li></ul></div></section><section><div class="container"><div class="closing-cta"><h2>Have a project in mind?</h2><p>Jane Doe is currently taking new engagements. Share a few details and we&#x27;ll find a time to talk.</p><a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:jane@example.test">Let&#x27;s work together</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="footer"><div class="container footer-inner"><span>© 2026 Jane Doe</span><span><a href="https://github.com/janedoe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a> · <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/janedoe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></span></div></footer></body></html>"
