"<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/><title>Jane Doe — Senior Software Engineer</title><meta name="description" content="Jane builds accessible, pixel-perfect interfaces for large-scale products."/><meta name="author" content="Jane Doe"/><link rel="canonical" href="https://jane.example.test"/><meta property="og:title" content="Jane Doe — Senior Software Engineer"/><meta property="og:description" content="Jane builds accessible, pixel-perfect interfaces for large-scale products."/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta property="og:url" content="https://jane.example.test"/><meta property="og:image" content="/og.png"/><meta property="og:image:width" content="1200"/><meta property="og:image:height" content="630"/><meta property="og:image:alt" content="Jane Doe — portfolio"/><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/><meta name="twitter:title" content="Jane Doe — Senior Software Engineer"/><meta name="twitter:description" content="Jane builds accessible, pixel-perfect interfaces for large-scale products."/><meta name="twitter:image" content="/og.png"/><style>/* fixture */</style></head><body><nav class="nav"><div class="nav-inner"><a href="/" class="nav-brand">jane-doe</a><ul class="nav-links"><li><a href="/">home</a></li><li><a href="/about/">about</a></li><li><a href="/projects/" class="active">projects</a></li><li><a href="/contact/">contact</a></li></ul></div></nav><main><section class="section"><div class="container"><p class="prompt">cd Signal Forge</p><h1>Signal Forge</h1><p style="color:var(--text-dim)"># A tool for crafting proof-backed portfolios.</p><p style="margin-top:8px"><a href="https://github.com/acme/signal-forge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">git@github.com:acme/signal-forge</a></p><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">./check-credibility.sh</p><ul class="pwb-credibility-byline" aria-label="Project credibility signals"><li class="pwb-credibility-chip"><span class="pwb-credibility-category">OSS Author</span></li><li class="pwb-credibility-chip"><span>23 contributors</span></li><li class="pwb-credibility-chip"><span title="This repo runs continuous integration on every push"><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span> CI</span></li><li class="pwb-credibility-chip"><span title="This repo declares a test framework"><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Tests</span></li><li class="pwb-credibility-chip"><span title="This repo publishes versioned releases"><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Releases</span></li><li class="pwb-credibility-chip"><a class="pwb-credibility-live" href="https://signal-forge.example.test" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Live <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">open demos/</p><section class="pwb-demos" aria-label="Demo"><figure class="pwb-demo pwb-demo-iframe"><div class="pwb-demo-aspect"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" title="Signal Forge in 90 seconds" loading="lazy" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" referrerPolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"></iframe></div><figcaption class="pwb-demo-caption">Signal Forge in 90 seconds</figcaption></figure></section></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat stack.json</p><div class="tag-group"><span class="tag">TypeScript</span><span class="tag">Next.js</span><span class="tag">Drizzle</span></div></div><div class="pwb-narrative pwb-narrative-toggle" data-pwb-scope="proj-1"><input type="radio" name="pwb-view-proj-1" id="pwb-view-recruiter-proj-1" class="pwb-narrative-radio pwb-narrative-radio-recruiter" aria-label="Recruiter view" checked=""/><input type="radio" name="pwb-view-proj-1" id="pwb-view-engineer-proj-1" class="pwb-narrative-radio pwb-narrative-radio-engineer" aria-label="Engineer view"/><div class="pwb-narrative-toggle-row" role="group" aria-label="Narrative view selection"><span class="pwb-narrative-toggle-label">view</span><label for="pwb-view-recruiter-proj-1" class="pwb-narrative-toggle-option pwb-narrative-toggle-option-recruiter">Recruiter</label><label for="pwb-view-engineer-proj-1" class="pwb-narrative-toggle-option pwb-narrative-toggle-option-engineer">Engineer</label></div><div class="pwb-narrative-pane pwb-narrative-pane-recruiter"><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat architecture.md</p><p class="pwb-narrative-text"><span class="pwb-sentence pwb-sentence-verified" data-pwb-status="verified">Edge-deployed static generator with a Postgres source of truth.</span></p></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat narrative.md</p><p class="pwb-narrative-text"><span class="pwb-sentence pwb-sentence-verified" data-pwb-status="verified">TypeScript end-to-end; React 18 + renderToStaticMarkup for templates.</span></p></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat deep-dive.md</p><p class="pwb-narrative-text"><span class="pwb-sentence pwb-sentence-flagged" data-pwb-status="flagged">The fact-extractor uses a two-pass LLM rubric with deterministic post-filters.</span></p></div></div><div class="pwb-narrative-pane pwb-narrative-pane-engineer"><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat architecture.md</p><p>Static-site generator targeting Cloudflare Pages; per-portfolio Pages Function carries the chatbot retrieval corpus.</p></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat narrative.md</p><p>Drizzle ORM against Postgres for the source-of-truth, server-side React renderToStaticMarkup for templates, BGE-large embeddings cached in jsonb for chatbot retrieval.</p></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat deep-dive.md</p><p>The fact-extractor uses a two-pass LLM rubric: extraction with structured-output JSON Schema, then deterministic post-filters to drop low-confidence facts and de-duplicate against existing rows.</p></div></div></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">cat tour.md</p><section class="pwb-storyboard" aria-label="Guided tour"><ol class="pwb-storyboard-grid"><li class="pwb-storyboard-card"><header class="pwb-storyboard-card-head"><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">💡</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-num">01</span><h4 class="pwb-storyboard-card-title">What it does</h4></header><p class="pwb-storyboard-card-desc">Turns a GitHub history into a proof-backed portfolio site.</p><ul class="pwb-storyboard-claims" aria-label="Verified claims"><li class="pwb-storyboard-claim"><span class="pwb-storyboard-marker pwb-storyboard-marker-ok" aria-label="Verified" title="The verifier confirmed this claim against repo state">✓</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-claim-label">Reads N projects per portfolio</span></li></ul></li><li class="pwb-storyboard-card"><header class="pwb-storyboard-card-head"><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛠</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-num">02</span><h4 class="pwb-storyboard-card-title">How it works</h4></header><p class="pwb-storyboard-card-desc">9-step pipeline: fetch → extract → narrate → verify.</p><ul class="pwb-storyboard-claims" aria-label="Verified claims"><li class="pwb-storyboard-claim"><span class="pwb-storyboard-marker pwb-storyboard-marker-ok" aria-label="Verified" title="The verifier confirmed this claim against repo state">✓</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-claim-label">Uses Drizzle for Postgres</span></li></ul></li><li class="pwb-storyboard-card"><header class="pwb-storyboard-card-head"><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">📄</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-num">03</span><h4 class="pwb-storyboard-card-title">Worth a look</h4></header><p class="pwb-storyboard-card-desc">The pipeline orchestrator: state machine + retries.</p><div class="pwb-storyboard-snippet"><p class="pwb-storyboard-snippet-path"><code>src/lib/pipeline/orchestrator.ts</code></p><pre class="pwb-storyboard-snippet-code"><code>export class PipelineOrchestrator { /* ... */ }</code></pre></div></li><li class="pwb-storyboard-card"><header class="pwb-storyboard-card-head"><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-num">04</span><h4 class="pwb-storyboard-card-title">Tested</h4></header><p class="pwb-storyboard-card-desc">Jest covers the helpers; integration tests cover the API.</p><ul class="pwb-storyboard-claims" aria-label="Verified claims"><li class="pwb-storyboard-claim"><span class="pwb-storyboard-marker pwb-storyboard-marker-ok" aria-label="Verified" title="The verifier confirmed this claim against repo state">✓</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-claim-label">1000+ unit tests</span></li></ul></li><li class="pwb-storyboard-card"><header class="pwb-storyboard-card-head"><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🚀</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-num">05</span><h4 class="pwb-storyboard-card-title">Deploys</h4></header><p class="pwb-storyboard-card-desc">Cloudflare Pages auto-provisions per portfolio.</p></li><li class="pwb-storyboard-card"><header class="pwb-storyboard-card-head"><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">▶</span><span class="pwb-storyboard-card-num">06</span><h4 class="pwb-storyboard-card-title">Try it</h4></header><p class="pwb-storyboard-card-desc">Click through to the live site.</p><div class="pwb-storyboard-demo"><a href="https://signal-forge.example.test" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="pwb-storyboard-demo-link">Try it <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a><pre class="pwb-storyboard-clone"><code>git clone https://github.com/acme/signal-forge</code></pre></div></li></ol><figure class="pwb-storyboard-diagram"><figcaption class="pwb-storyboard-diagram-summary">Architecture</figcaption><pre class="mermaid pwb-storyboard-diagram-source">graph TD
  A[Repo] --&gt; B[Pipeline]
  B --&gt; C[Static Site]</pre><p class="pwb-storyboard-diagram-hint">Diagram source rendered with <a href="https://mermaid.js.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mermaid.js</a>.</p></figure><script>(function(){try{if(typeof window==="undefined"||typeof document==="undefined")return;var nodes=document.querySelectorAll("pre.mermaid");if(!nodes||nodes.length===0)return;import("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10/dist/mermaid.esm.min.mjs").then(function(m){var mermaid=m.default;mermaid.initialize({startOnLoad:false,securityLevel:"strict",theme:"default"});mermaid.run({nodes:nodes}).then(function(){nodes.forEach(function(n){var p=n.parentElement;if(p)p.setAttribute("data-pwb-mermaid-rendered","true");});}).catch(function(){});}).catch(function(){});}catch(e){}})();</script></section></div><div class="project-section"><p class="prompt">grep -h &#x27;^Fact:&#x27; notes/</p><section class="pwb-evidence-list" aria-label="Verified facts"><ul class="pwb-evidence-items"><li class="pwb-evidence-item"><div class="pwb-evidence-claim"><div class="pwb-evidence-claim-line"><span class="pwb-evidence-tick" aria-label="Verified by the pipeline" title="This claim has been verified against the source">✓</span><span class="pwb-evidence-claim-text">Written in TypeScript</span><span class="pwb-evidence-source" title="Evidence type: dependency">from package.json</span></div><details class="pwb-evidence-details"><summary class="pwb-evidence-summary">Evidence</summary><div class="pwb-evidence-body"><blockquote class="pwb-evidence-quote">&quot;typescript&quot;: &quot;^5.4.0&quot; in package.json</blockquote><p class="pwb-evidence-ref"><span class="pwb-evidence-ref-label">Source:</span> <code>package.json</code></p></div></details></div></li><li class="pwb-evidence-item"><div class="pwb-evidence-claim"><div class="pwb-evidence-claim-line"><span class="pwb-evidence-tick" aria-label="Verified by the pipeline" title="This claim has been verified against the source">✓</span><span cla